      • saveReservations

        public Document saveReservations(Document rup,
                                 boolean checkOnly,
                                 boolean resourceChange)
                          throws ResourceGatewayException,
                                 JDOMException,
                                 java.io.IOException
        Saves all reservation XML elements of the ResourceUtilisationPlan, depending on "reservation.planningStatus" (see rup.xsd for the XML data model) and removes or updates older reservations for the case and for each activity. Then sets planning status and error or warning values on XML elements (e.g. if a resource cannot be reserved or technical errors occur) and returns the ResourceUtilisationPlan.
        Parameters:
        rup -
        checkOnly -
        resourceChange -
        Throws:
        ResourceGatewayException
        JDOMException
